> Whether you have one for breakfast, a post-workout boost, or a quick snack, these ready-to-blend smoothies are just the treat you need. This assortment features three fruitiest flavors: Peachy Mango, Banana Berry, and Acai-Cherry Berry. To enjoy one of these fruit-packed, no-sugar-added blends, all you have to do is blend them with the liquid of your choice (we like whole milk, almond milk, or oat milk) until smooth and enjoy!

Fill a #cup{} with @milk{200%ml} or @water{200%ml} - liquid of your choice.

Pour @Peachy Mango Ready-to-Blend Smoothie{2%unit}, @Banana Berry Ready-to-Blend Smoothie{2%unit}, and @Acai-Cherry Berry Ready-to-Blend Smoothie{2%unit} contents into #blender{}; blend until smooth.

Return to the cup and enjoy!

> To ensure the highest quality when you receive your smoothies, they will come in a separate box from your meals. Your Ready-to-Blend Smoothie box may arrive a few days after your meal box. Smoothies should be stored frozen.